{"tid":442021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！羅哲斯向港府發律師信 促交代被拒入境原因","createTime":"2017-10-20T08:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T05:17:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":131,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"191d7e21266b20ae378a1143366587558f76cbf4","tid":442021,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）本月11日被拒入境香港，觸發中英外交風波，令國際關注一國兩制在香港的落實情況。繼英國首相文翠珊開腔稱外交部已向中國及香港政府提出交涉，羅哲斯告知《蘋果》已委托在香港的代表律師向港府發律師信，要求港府交代上周拒絕他入境的原因。他表示在收到入境處處長回覆後，將公開有關信件內容。<br />\n<br />\n羅哲斯上周被拒入境時，民主黨前立法會議員兼律師何俊仁曾坐列車趕到機場，希望提供協助。羅哲斯亦曾向本報確認，已委託何俊仁就他被拒入境一事向政府提出進一步查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57355807&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57355807%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171020&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=399f1ca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57355807%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171020&h=cba9fcae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57355807&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171020</a>"},{"pid":"579b88deda26d017516fd480f5f35649658efb10","tid":442021,"uid":102842,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）本月11日被拒入境香港，觸發中英外交風波，令國際關注一國兩制在香港