一事向政府提出進一步查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57355807&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57355807%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171020&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=399f1ca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57355807%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171020&h=cba9fcae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57355807&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171020</a></blockquote><br />\n委託個廢既...........</blockquote><br />\n可能一齊去睇av"},{"pid":"6336ed5910f7f65a7e1383a0c4f6680ec52dde40","tid":442021,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"突咩發，淋病都唔會理"},{"pid":"0f3d7aa860c571f0ae0878583bb075d5fafc231a","tid":442021,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"口交部出咗聲未？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港內政不容許其它強國說三道四 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c39a340f2433958b75d107504733a3368976bb9","tid":442021,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家英國政府就係唔肯認一國兩制盪然無存<br />\n因為係律師信關係，香港政府嘅答覆必須正面回答<br />\n而答案好大可能係證明一國兩制有問題<br />\n到時佢地同英國政府gargain就更加有力</blockquote><br />\n英國都要含中共撚，你咪天真喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要含撚拎著數都要睇自己有咩牌起手，自己政界大佬俾人咁落面，就咁算仲成世界？人地仲點要人買英國帳</blockquote><br />\n比面就比面啦買咩帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要用又用錯  係賣帳唔係買帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買帳係領情<br />\n賣帳係比面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n含撚呢個行為本身就係賣帳<br />\n支國俾人含完賣返生意俾英國佬<br />\n但支國擺既態度一直係聯合聲明廢左<br />\n香港係內部事務英國外人死開<br />\n換句話說即係英國對<br />\n香港完全冇立場出聲=冇左香港呢張牌<br />\n再深入講就係支國唔駛出錢要英國賣支國帳唔打香港牌，因為本來就冇<br />\n要幫人含都要睇自己係邊個<br />\n如果英默認左佢冇立場出聲<br />\n佢就真係再冇野賣，佢再想含都只會係欣宜俾支國踢開"},{"pid":"49ea5a274800835a155974c2a4b21e626cbf82a8","tid":442021,"uid":63669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:21:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係弱智黎 , 人地做野就話無用唔做野就話驚左中國唔理香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BNO如果平到權一定要禁曬呢班垃圾"},{"pid":"d621c54fe2c3436351ca2f265ebd866bdb978c59","tid":442021,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e572b34cbcf3963fd4fac37b3323d3b3e295187","tid":442021,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔真係弱智黎 , 人地做野就話無用唔做野就話驚左中國唔理香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BNO如果平到權一定要禁曬呢班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n咁事實就咁出封信真係無用喎,以今時今日既中共你覺得真係會理你英國譴責？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非聯同歐盟,美國等大國全面制裁支那啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係要搞，由美國出面黎真的威脅要收回香港既特別地位就可以了，中國冇左香港會做中間會好撚大獲（當然歐美都唔會好過所以唔多可能成事）"},{"pid":"f55df46f430c1fd78d2cd541c6887b6b02967bea","tid":442021,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"港府應立即宣佈要求匯豐24小時內結束在港業務以懲罰條白鬼咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031bad88500eea9d4f39bad663a07f687f3f26a3","tid":442021,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔真係弱智黎 , 人地做野就話無用唔做野就話驚左中國唔理香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BNO如果平到權一定要禁曬呢班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n咁事實就咁出封信真係無用喎,以今時今日既中共你覺得真係會理你英國譴責？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /